description:
We're dissecting the 3 stills released from the upcoming anime film "The Lord of the Rings: The War of the Rohirrim"!  We'll analyze (and over-analyze) these images to see what clues we can discover and note some initial observations about the first new Middle-earth film in 10 years!

War of the Rohirrim releases December 13, 2024.

#waroftherohirrim #lordoftherings #lotr
title: War of the Rohirrim First Images BREAKDOWN
